To edit and generate GUI elements we use the GLUON SceneBuilder for JavaFX in it's actual Version which is the GUI Builder for JavaFX MVC and MVVM Concepts is. We can use this concept also as mvvm model (mvvm concept by Carl Dea) when needed.
